2.0.name: wordpress/wp-complete-backup
2.0.description:
WP Backup Complete is an easy to use, complete backup solution for WordPress. The plugin offers the ability to backup the database as well as make a complete file system backup.

Plugin features:

  • Automatic backup restore tool
  • One-click button to clear all stored backups
  • Option to delete backups individually
  • Complete user guide in PDF format
  • Access to community support forum
  • Randomized server storage locations
